description:
The famous Australian multi-instrumentalist James Morrison (trumpet/trombone/piano, etc.) on the International Jazz Festival 2018 in Mariinsky-2 theatre, Saint-Petersburg, Russia, April 30
---
In this piece James tells about how to get into the orchestra and how to practice properly
